Each pipeline in actions/ (called "an action") must be a step with no input,
and a primary output "result", and an option "repo" (that says on which repo
to act).  It must have a primary parameters port as well (and must defined the
parameters it accepts).  The step type must be "client:action-{action}", and
its file name "actions/{action}.xproc".

An action must provide ... (xml + text...)
